==== ENTRY 4 ====
HEADWORD: Lister
<hw>List"er</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧st"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>List</er> a strip, border, prob. applied to the furrow or the ridge
of earth along the furrow.]</ety> <def>A double-moldboard plow which
throws a deep furrow, and at the same time plants and covers grain in
the bottom of the furrow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Listerian</ent>⟦br⟧
